{"id":"h_mr5k39hu_ww0o","text":"When the user says \"ascii galaxy\" or \"/galaxy\" they mean the pi TUI extension ~/.pi/agent/extensions/void-blackhole.ts, not the ~/Developer/galaxy website (which is the lensed-blackhole personal site).","scope":"global","project":null,"category":"correction","created":"2026-07-03T23:20:08.658Z","lastReinforced":"2026-07-03T23:20:08.658Z","hits":0,"source":"agent","pinned":false}
{"id":"h_mr5kynpe_iaxba5d0","text":"When calling learn_heuristic, always supply the required basis field (user-confirmed, directly-observed, reproduced, or documented) attesting how the lesson was verified true, per DESIGN.md section 3 of the heuristics extension.","scope":"global","project":null,"category":"workflow","created":"2026-07-03T23:44:33.410Z","lastReinforced":"2026-07-03T23:44:33.410Z","hits":0,"source":"agent","pinned":false,"basis":"documented"}
{"id":"h_mr5kywqu_mhwrir7u","text":"some user lesson for basis QA verification test","scope":"global","project":null,"category":"workflow","created":"2026-07-03T23:44:45.126Z","lastReinforced":"2026-07-03T23:44:45.126Z","hits":0,"source":"user","pinned":false,"basis":"user-confirmed"}
{"id":"h_mr5kyyur_n3mdadfi","text":"In pi extensions, pi.sendMessage always injects the custom message into LLM context on the next request (persisted as a custom-message entry); the `display` field controls only TUI visibility, not context inclusion — for display-only ephemeral output use ctx.ui.setWidget()/custom(), and for out-of-context persistent state use pi.appendEntry().","scope":"global","project":null,"category":"gotcha","created":"2026-07-03T23:44:47.859Z","lastReinforced":"2026-07-03T23:44:47.859Z","hits":0,"source":"agent","pinned":false,"basis":"directly-observed"}
